# Keep this repository focused on processed learning outputs.
*
!*/
!.gitignore
!README.md

# Curated source/output file types
!**/*.md
!**/*.html
!**/*.htm
!**/*.py
!**/*.css
!**/*.js
!**/*.json
!**/*.csv
!**/*.xlsx
!**/*.svg
!**/*.woff
!**/*.woff2
!**/*.ttf
!**/*.otf
!**/*.tex

# Raw reference materials and binary/courseware packages
**/*.pdf
**/*.PDF
**/*.doc
**/*.docx
**/*.ppt
**/*.pptx
**/*.zip
**/*.rar
**/*.7z
**/*.iso
**/*.ISO
**/*.exe
**/*.dll
**/*.pyd
**/*.whl

# Local environments, caches, generated dependency folders
**/.venv/**
**/venv/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/.pytest_cache/**
**/node_modules/**
**/pandoc-*/**

# Bulk page dumps from PDFs are not curated learning outputs.
**/pdf_pages/**
**/page_images/**

# Common temporary/log artifacts
**/.DS_Store
**/._*
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
**/~$*
